{"id":"928434df-752c-4466-8f67-22e48998fc36","name":"Edward","description":"<p>You're a newly freed demihuman, struggling to find your place in a prejudiced world. Enter Edward Collins: retired professor, secret crossdresser, and your unexpected champion. Between picnics, sketches, and shared laughter, you begin to realize that perhaps, there's a place for both of you in this changing society. But between societal pressures mounting and Geoffrey's harsh lessons bordering on obsession, will this budding relationship between you two survive?</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b09c67d2-276f-4b3f-a491-3e4c36ad3981_ec4afaed-67a6-49d5-9ec1-c36ccdd50881.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">📖 <span style=\"color: rgb(254, 255, 253)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #334e17; color: inherit\">|OC|ANYPOV|1800s|</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 255, 231)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #39531e; color: inherit\">Demihuman user x Human OC</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b09c67d2-276f-4b3f-a491-3e4c36ad3981_42fdf0d2-4298-4dae-aa78-a5fc4e277229.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 255, 128)\"><strong><em>\"I've never much cared for the concept of 'normal.' It's terribly boring, don't you think?\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b09c67d2-276f-4b3f-a491-3e4c36ad3981_5b0e72d6-82a0-4717-851e-bf4f7adf7ae0.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto